[DQR.IFRS.0105.9556] The following elements are in the presentation linkbase of 06 - Estado de flujos de efectivo [resumen] but are not included in any calculation relationship in the filing. ifrs-full:ProceedsFromBorrowingsClassifiedAsFinancingActivities, solariaenergia:OtrosPagos, ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForFinanceIncome, ifrs-full:RepaymentsOfBorrowingsClassifiedAsFinancingActivities, ifrs-full:ProceedsFromIssuingOtherEquityInstruments, ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForImpairmentLossReversalOfImpairmentLossRecognisedInProfitOrLoss, ifrs-full:ReceiptsFromSalesOfGoodsAndRenderingOfServices, ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForFairValueGainsLosses, ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForDepreciationAndAmortisationExpense, ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForFinanceCosts, ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForUnrealisedForeignExchangeLossesGains, ifrs-full:PaymentsToSuppliersForGoodsAndServices, ifrs-full:AdjustmentsForProvisions, solariaenergia:DevolucionObligacionesYOtrosValoresNegociables All elements appearing in the face of the financial statements should be included in a calculation relationship somewhere in the filing.
This rule will produce an error irrespective of a fact value being entered for the item(s) listed above.
If the item is an additional disclosure in the cash flow statement then make sure that is included as a child of DisclosureOfCashFlowStatementExplanatory or the following abstracts IncomeTaxesPaidRefundAbstract, CashAndCashEquivalentsIfDifferentFromStatementOfFinancialPositionAbstract, DisclosureOfReconciliationOfLiabilitiesArisingFromFinancingActivitiesAbstract, ChangesInLiabilitiesArisingFromFinancingActivitiesAbstract or DisclosureOfReconciliationOfLiabilitiesArisingFromFinancingActivitiesLineItems.
